# Minecraft Fabric Mod Development Skill

## Overview

Fabric is a **modular, lightweight modding toolchain** for Minecraft: Java Edition 1.14+.
Core components:
- **Fabric Loader** – Loads mods at runtime, handles mod metadata
- **Fabric API** – Cross-compatibility hooks, events, utilities on top of vanilla
- **Fabric Loom** – Gradle plugin for deobfuscated dev environment
- **Yarn / Mojang Mappings** – Human-readable name mappings for Minecraft internals
- **Mixin** – Bytecode injection library to modify Minecraft classes at runtime
- **MixinExtras** – Bundled since Loader 0.15; provides compatible, precise injectors

Always check latest versions at: https://fabricmc.net/develop/

