## 13. Common Gotchas

| Problem | Fix |
|---|---|
| Items/blocks invisible in game | Missing model JSON or blockstate JSON |
| Crash on startup | Check `fabric.mod.json` entrypoint class path |
| Mixin not applying | Verify `mymod.mixins.json` lists the mixin class, check method descriptor |
| `NullPointerException` on server side | Check `level.isClientSide()` before client-only calls |
| `assets.[modid]` directory not found | Use `/` not `.` in path: `assets/mymod/` |
| Desync (client/server disagree) | Send packets to sync state; never modify server state from client directly |
| Networking crash | Packet handlers must dispatch to main thread via `.execute()` |
| `@Redirect` breaks with other mods | Use MixinExtras `@WrapOperation` instead |

